---
// PricingTable — the locked Variant D mockup. Three peer modes (Embed / Retain / Own),
// equal visual weight, bidirectional ↔ arrows between. No "destination" emphasis;
// clients move between modes as projects evolve. Widens beyond the 680px thesis
// content-width via negative margins; stacks 1-col on mobile with arrow rotation +
// caption glyph swap (↔ → ↕). Locked 2026-05-27 via /plan-design-review.
//
// Mockup reference:
//   ~/.gstack/projects/WujiLabs-wujilabs.dev/designs/wuji-labs-pricing-20260527/
//   variant-D-peer-modes.html
---

<div class="pricing-wrap">
  <div class="modes">
    <div class="mode">
      <span class="mode-name">Embed</span>
      <span class="mode-cost"><s>$5k</s>$3k<span class="unit">/mo</span></span>
      <span class="mode-mode">On-site or screen-share</span>
      <p class="mode-body">Build the collaboration space plus the coaching and tools training to use it. Real-time contact across a team. Usually 1–2 months per build, but you can stay in Embed as long as new work justifies it.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="arrow" aria-hidden="true">↔</div>
    <div class="mode">
      <span class="mode-name">Retain</span>
      <span class="mode-cost"><s>$2.5k</s>$1.5k<span class="unit">/mo</span></span>
      <span class="mode-mode">Remote, async</span>
      <p class="mode-body">Ongoing changes, new connectors, evolving the space as you change. Includes about an hour a week of coaching or training. Cancel anytime; re-engage when something new comes up.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="arrow" aria-hidden="true">↔</div>
    <div class="mode">
      <span class="mode-name">Own</span>
      <span class="mode-cost">$0<span class="unit">/mo</span></span>
      <span class="mode-mode">Your hardware, your keys</span>
      <p class="mode-body">Stop paying anytime and it keeps running — on your hardware, yours to keep. Nothing degrades, nothing gets locked. The 互不从属 (mutual non-subordination) commitment lives in the contract structure here, not just the marketing.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <p class="mode-note"><span class="mode-arrow-glyph" aria-hidden="true">↔</span> Many clients flow Embed → Retain → Own as a build settles, then back to Retain or Embed when a new project shows up. The arrows are a hint, not a path.</p>
</div>

<style>
  /* Widen beyond the thesis 680px content-width via negative margins.
     Stays inside the article flow; no global layout change. */
  .pricing-wrap {
    max-width: 940px;
    margin: calc(var(--space-unit) * 4) auto;
    margin-left: calc((var(--content-width-thesis) - 940px) / 2);
    margin-right: calc((var(--content-width-thesis) - 940px) / 2);
  }
  .modes {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr auto 1fr;
    align-items: stretch;
    gap: 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }
  .mode {
    padding: calc(var(--space-unit) * 4) calc(var(--space-unit) * 3);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: calc(var(--space-unit) * 1.5);
  }
  .mode-name {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .mode-cost {
    font-family: 'Source Sans 3', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }
  .mode-cost s { color: var(--text-3); margin-right: calc(var(--space-unit) * 0.5); font-weight: 400; font-size: 0.95rem; }
  .mode-cost .unit { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-2); font-weight: 400; }
  .mode-mode {
    font-family: 'Source Sans 3', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--text-3);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }
  .mode-body {
    font-size: 0.93rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--text-2);
    margin-top: calc(var(--space-unit) * 0.5);
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
  /* Bidirectional ↔ arrow between columns. Subdued, decorative. */
  .arrow {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--text-3);
    font-family: 'Source Sans 3', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    padding: 0 calc(var(--space-unit) * 0.5);
  }
  .mode-note {
    font-family: 'Source Sans 3', sans-serif;
    color: var(--text-2);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: calc(var(--space-unit) * 2) auto 0;
    max-width: var(--content-width-thesis);
    font-style: italic;
    text-align: center;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .pricing-wrap { margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 100%; }
    .modes { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .arrow {
      padding: 0;
      transform: rotate(90deg);
      min-height: calc(var(--space-unit) * 3);
    }
    /* Caption arrow glyph swaps to vertical to match the rotated table arrows */
    .mode-arrow-glyph {
      font-size: 0;
    }
    .mode-arrow-glyph::before {
      content: '↕';
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
